Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去學校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可能一直請病假不去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:16.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,準備這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用為我這麼費心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想這樣做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你喜歡上我啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可以想色色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:35.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我為你做晚飯等你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這個家裡休息就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特意去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？ 這樣才能感覺到我在報答你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉每次幹勁十足想做什麼的時候總是給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:59.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,微波爐 高壓鍋 空調都是自己壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你用得太粗魯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:03.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有那麼用力…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要你用力氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的機器真脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 請你老老實實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:15.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:19.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:29.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 打你手機都不接所以就過來看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不許看！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:31.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:32.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:45.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別為難大病初癒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你和以前一樣是裝病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:57.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依倒是覺得依人的品味很前衛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依 不用安慰我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊再見 下次再來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛才來沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊 姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名你明明不用一起出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人今天樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你很慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏這方面那麼敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是對蒼乃也不能說的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在隱瞞什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有 也不用真名來亂猜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再說根本就沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:08.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是適合兒童套餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭這種玩笑 聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:38.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你有沒有考慮過接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒考慮過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看都沾上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡來了 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:57.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幫您拿新的紙巾來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:01.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸一起吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是很晚回來所以吃飯也很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,您的工作真是非常忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他自己安排不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以對爸爸說這樣的話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,若是不對男人這樣說他們是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是很複雜的一個家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是很複雜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:46.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,領養無依無靠的孩子來照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是你剛剛設定的想像？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 神秘的鬍子紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 原來你比較中意年長的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 加班呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這個是新產品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,酪梨口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種拉麵怎麼能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難得在大減價的時候買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被壓倉貨給誘惑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我對購物很在行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不是說過不用準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你太晚回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,車站前的超市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你又跑出去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要太陽沒出來就不要緊的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指這個 會發生像上次那樣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不覺得無聊就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對心臟不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今不用你來說我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是還是擔心茉莉你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,給我好好聽別人說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是來送報紙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我說屋主馬上就會回來 所以就叫他過會兒送來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你訂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上 還有他說我很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還送我洗衣粉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說是連頑固油漬都能洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我去開門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了 現在就來開門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要鎖上門？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是要鎖門的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,以前不是都不鎖的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 將來每個人的防範意識非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 算了 你還沒吃晚飯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在慌張什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你偏偏今天來啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最近你的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去了醫院後也是馬上就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是… 身體不怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就更該幫你做點熱騰騰的飯菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經很晚了 真名的家人也會擔心你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你做好晚飯後就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經吃過了 剛剛吃好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,盡是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:43.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這一堆泡麵是怎麼回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉在樓上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:09.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼… 在想明天的天空會不會是藍天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:16.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一段日子沒來 你居然全在吃泡麵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的這款很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,瞎說 正是因為吃了這些所以身體才變壞的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就讓你吃點好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微弄弄就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你還是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是酪梨拉麵的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備在那裡站多久啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒… 有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名小姐 水開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還算蒙混得過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直這樣繼續下去 我也堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我為什麼要那麼慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓姊姊為這點事擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,醬油沒有了 砂糖和鹽也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前全被我打翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,胡椒 醋和醬料都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這些也都被我打翻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前都打翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你現在去買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因為我要為依人做美味的土豆燉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒調味料也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,超市已經關門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,車站前有24小時的便利商店對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:43.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼快去快回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉那傢伙絕對不要出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原以為依人肯定藏了些什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚… 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊 一個禮拜之前你就住這了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大致上是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他都讓你做些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我還真是清閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有人會這樣說自己的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你替換衣服怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是依人幫我準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,內衣的話就自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真傷腦筋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,每天這些都用手洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部要手洗的時候你怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,洗的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,洗的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:44.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:45.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有做過色色的事情 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:02.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你能為我解釋一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 她是我表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的 在我找到公寓之前先在這住幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什麼要對我隱瞞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和我也是初次見面 不都沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上我很緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可沒看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋的人是我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你也應該早點和我串供好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你該說的話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是依人的什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來… 是什麼人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的沒有想過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園在教堂不是發生了這個那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到… 到底那個是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說她餓了很困擾 我就收留她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,棄貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再添一碗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,土豆燉肉實在太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,慢待了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話我就可以把不太可靠的依人交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可靠的到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個看起來都不怎麼可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾也收拾不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰在增加垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還很色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還經常發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最近煩惱的事情增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她看起來不像壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話太多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你的責任！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那麼不信任我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不告訴我 我怎麼來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:45.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 把她撿回來以後由貓變身成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了在未來世界改變我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓姊姊擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 就是因為這個所以連我都要隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為真名是大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不讓我說我是不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在住院中 從以前開始身體就比較虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:19.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 那我就不追究事情的根本了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你們有其它原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事我不會對任何人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教 茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,話還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的兩人時間 我怎麼可以打擾你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得是個不可思議的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是不可思議呢還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找茉莉多說點話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:28.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話我就可以把不太可靠的依人交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她說過儘量不要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該馬上就回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼說得那麼輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉小姐她不準備回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會這樣想啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人你太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說去找…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該還沒走遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能總是靠借衣服來生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 接下來你們要去約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你們是情侶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,情侶？ 你說誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人是個寂寞的單身漢對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我現在這樣 有時候也會有人向我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的最近是什麼時候的事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小學四年級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 就這樣先安心住下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我就再住一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我又沒特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你這「好了」是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒見森宮同學準時到校了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:50.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說為什麼只跟真名打招呼啊？ 可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你在笑什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:32.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:33.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小依
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來段繞口令吧
